@startuml 07-sequence-mvvm
title MVVM-architectuur: lid upgradet abonnement (Basic -> Unlimited)
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Lid" as User
boundary "MemberSubscriptionScreen\n(@Composable - View)" as View
control "MemberSessionViewModel\n(ViewModel)" as VM
collections "MemberSessionState\n(observable state)" as State
participant "SportClubApiService\n(RealApiService - Model/API-laag)" as Api
participant "Ktor Backend" as Backend

== Initieel laden ==
View -> VM : LaunchedEffect ->\nloadMemberInfo(memberId)
activate VM
VM -> Api : getMember(memberId)
activate Api
Api -> Backend : GET /api/v1/users/me\n(Authorization: Bearer <token>)
Backend --> Api : 200 OK (UserResponse incl. membership)
Api --> VM : Member(activeMembership = Membership(\n  type=BASIC, billingCycle=YEARLY,\n  startDate=..., endDate=..., status=ACTIVE))
deactivate Api
VM -> State : state = state.copy(memberInfo = member)
deactivate VM
State --> View : recomposition\n(observes "state by mutableStateOf")
View -> User : toont huidig plan,\nstartdatum, einddatum,\n"Upgrade to Unlimited"-knop

== Gebruiker klikt "Upgrade to Unlimited" ==
User -> View : klik [Upgrade to Unlimited]
View -> VM : upgrade(memberId, membership.id)
activate VM
VM -> Api : upgradeMembership(membershipId)
activate Api
Api -> Backend : PUT /api/v1/memberships/{id}/upgrade\n(Authorization: Bearer <token>)
activate Backend
Backend -> Backend : MembershipService.upgradeMembership(id)\n- valideer: huidig type != Unlimited\n- (toekomstig) bereken naar-rato verschil\n  bij Yearly billing
Backend --> Api : 200 OK (MembershipResponse\n type=Unlimited, ...)
deactivate Backend
Api --> VM : Membership(type = UNLIMITED, ...)
deactivate Api

alt succes
  VM -> VM : loadMemberInfo(memberId)\n(herlaadt member + membership)
  VM -> State : state = state.copy(error = null)
  VM -> View : onDone(true)
else fout (bv. al Unlimited)
  VM -> State : state = state.copy(error = e.message)
  VM -> View : onDone(false)
end
deactivate VM

State --> View : recomposition
View -> User : toont bijgewerkt plan\n("Unlimited - Yearly")\nof foutmelding
@enduml
